social_posts.post_text: Élucidation online now for free! - @ian.t.hamilton  created a thoughtful piece about the meaning of skiing to him, and us. - Link in my bio, check it out! - It was an honour to be apart of this project. We had some tough times filming this, through Covid set backs to injuries. But still managed to let the passion flow and get something done. 👊🏻
Let’s do it like they do it on discovery eh
Found alone, far from home. But really close.
Flat light , flat frontside … Ain’t no sunshine
Quick rip to Mexico with my partner in crime was well worth it! 🌅 🏝️ ☀️ 🐢 🍷 🍻 🐊 🌮 🌶️ •• Got it all in before I got under the knife. Thanks for a great time @neusnow 😘
Been missing creating media like this! • Taken some time to live differently, heal my body, and let love in 🥰 • But the itch is back, keep an eye out later this winter 😏
Coupla classics and some bendy knees 👌
Thankful 🙏🏻 • Health 🍎 • Family 👫 • Friends 🎉 • Neus ❤️ •••• didn’t think I’d get to finish the year skiing, let alone a few pow turns! 🙏🏻
The Saturday morning one and done ⬇️ 🎤 • 🙏🏻 ✌️
I hope you find your fix •
